\c 21
\s Rwiyo rokuvonga pamusoro pokukunda
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Mambo uchafara nesimba renyu, Jehovha; Achafarira kuponesa kwenyu zvikuru sei!
\v 2 Makamupa zvakadikanwa nomwoyo wake, Hamuna kuramba kukumbira kwemiromo yake.
\v 3 Nokuti munomuchingura nemikomborero yezvakanaka; Munodzika korona yendarama yakaisvonaka pamusoro wake.
\v 4 Akakumbira upenyu kwamuri, mukamupa ihwo; Namazuva mazhinji nokusingaperi-peri.
\v 5 Kurumbidzwa kwake kukuru
\s nokuda
\s kwokuponesa kwenyu,
\s Makaisa pamusoro pake kukudzwa noumambo.
\p
\v 6 Nokuti munomukomborera zvikuru nokusingaperi;
\s Munomufadza nomufaro pamberi penyu.
\p
\v 7 Nokuti mambo anovimba
\s naJehovha,
\s Nounyoro hoWokumusorosoro haangazunguswi.
\p
\v 8 Ruoko rwenyu ruchawana vavengi venyu vose;
\s Ruoko rwenyu rworudyi ruchawana vose vanokuvengai.
\p
\v 9 Muchavaita sevira romoto nenguva yokutsamwa kwenyu.
\s Jehovha achavamedza nehasha dzake,
\s Moto uchavaparadza.
